  <url type="homepage">https://axi.chat</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://gitlab.com/axichat/axichat/-/issues</url>
  <url type="vcs-browser">https://gitlab.com/axichat/axichat</url>
  <update_contact>support_AT_axi.chat</update_contact>
  <description>
    <p>Axichat is a free open source SMTP (email) and XMPP (chat) client with cutting-edge UI.</p>
    <p>You can self-host your own email and XMPP server for Axichat if you want extra privacy and control.</p>
    <p>Feature highlights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unified inbox for chat + email</li>
      <li>Sync across all your devices (mobile and desktop)</li>
      <li>Easy drag-and-drop calendar</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Axichat is still under active development, so things may break.</p>
  </description>
